18#include "ReedSolomonEncoder.h"
19#include "GenericGF.h"
20
21#include <stdexcept>
22#include <algorithm>
23#include <iterator>
24
25namespace ZXing {
26
27ReedSolomonEncoder::ReedSolomonEncoder(const GenericGF& field)
28: _field(&field)
29{
30 _cachedGenerators.push_back(GenericGFPoly(field, { 1 }));
31}
32
33const GenericGFPoly&
34ReedSolomonEncoder::buildGenerator(int degree)
35{
36 int cachedGenSize = Size(_cachedGenerators);
37 if (degree >= cachedGenSize) {
38 GenericGFPoly lastGenerator = _cachedGenerators.back();
39 for (int d = cachedGenSize; d <= degree; d++) {
40 lastGenerator.multiply(GenericGFPoly(*_field, { 1, _field->exp(d - 1 + _field->generatorBase()) }));
41 _cachedGenerators.push_back(lastGenerator);
42 }
43 }
44
45 return *std::next(_cachedGenerators.begin(), degree);
46}
47
48void
49ReedSolomonEncoder::encode(std::vector<int>& toEncode, const int ecBytes)
50{
51 if (ecBytes == 0) {
52 throw std::invalid_argument("No error correction bytes");
53 }
54 int dataBytes = Size(toEncode) - ecBytes;
55 if (dataBytes <= 0) {
56 throw std::invalid_argument("No data bytes provided");
57 }
58 GenericGFPoly info = GenericGFPoly(*_field, std::vector<int>(toEncode.begin(), toEncode.begin() + dataBytes));
59 info.multiplyByMonomial(ecBytes, 1);
60 GenericGFPoly _;
61 info.divide(buildGenerator(ecBytes), _);
62 auto& coefficients = info.coefficients();
63 int numZeroCoefficients = ecBytes - Size(coefficients);
64 std::fill_n(toEncode.begin() + dataBytes, numZeroCoefficients, 0);
65 std::copy(coefficients.begin(), coefficients.end(), toEncode.begin() + dataBytes + numZeroCoefficients);
66}
